Class DotEffect

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.soen6441.core.effect.Effect
      • com.soen6441.core.effect.DotEffect
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TimerListener

    public class DotEffect
extends Effect
implements TimerListener
    This is a kind of special effect on critter. By adding this effect to a critter object, to add a DOT on the critter object.
